<plot>This short emphasizes the many ways that Ecuador is building for the future, by constructing new roadways, railroads, and factories; and by attracting foreign investment. New agricultural methods are being used that will increase Ecuador's exports of produce. In Cuenca, we see weavers making Panama hats, 75% of which are produced here.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?561347</url></doc>
